high_descs: Turn left to go to the counter next to the brass trash can.
Pick up the gray knife on the counter
Turn around and go to the left side of the white table on the left.
Put the potato behind the paper towel.
Turn around the face the counter on the right of the stove.
Place the gray knife on the left of the fork.
Turn around towards the white table again.
Take one slice of the potato from the table.
Go around the table to the refrigerator.
Chill the potato on the shelf above the gray bowl and take it out.
Turn around and go to the front of the white table on the right.
Place the potato slice on the right side of the green sponge in front of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of potato on the table.

high_descs: Walk towards the counter next to the trash can
Grab a knife from the counter
Walk with the knife towards the white table
Slice the potato behind the paper roll on the table
Turn around and walk towards the stove counter
Put knife on the counter
Walk towards the white table
Grab a slice of potato from the table
Walk the the potato slice towards the fridge
Put the potato slice in the fridge, close the door and take the slice from the fridge
Walk with the potato slice towards the white table
Put the potato slice on the table
anns.task_desc: Slice the potato, grab a slice, put it in the fridge, put it on the table

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn right and walk to the table on the right.
Slice the tomato behind the paper towels on the table.
Turn around face the stove.
Put the knife on the counter to the right of the stove.
Turn back around and face the table.
Take a potato slice on the table.
Turn right, then left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the slice inside, then close the door. Wait a few seconds, then remove the slice and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the table on the right.
Place the slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a refridgerated potato slice on the table.
